from sklearn.datasets import load_breast_cancer

X, y = load_breast_cancer(True)
pd_X, pd_y = pd.DataFrame(X, columns=['x' + str(i) for i in range(X.shape[1])
                                      ]), pd.DataFrame(y, columns=['target'])
data = pd.concat([pd_X, pd_y], axis=1)

from sklearn.model_selection import train_test_split
from sklearn.pipeline import Pipeline

X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(cancer.iloc[:, :-1],
                                                    cancer.iloc[:, -1])
pipe = Pipeline([('scaler', MinMaxScaler()), ('knn', KNeighborsClassifier())])
pipe.fit(X_train, y_train)
pipe.score(X_test, y_test)

from sklearn.decomposition import PCA

temp = []
for i in range(cancer.shape[1] - 2, 1, -1):
    pca = PCA(i)
    x = pca.fit_transform(cancer.iloc[:, :-1])
    t = cross_val_score(KNeighborsClassifier(), x, cancer.iloc[:, -1], cv=10)
    temp.append(np.mean(t))

    pipe = Pipeline([('scaler', MinMaxScaler()), ('pca', PCA(i)),
                     ('rbf', RandomForestClassifier(100))])

from sklearn.datasets import load_iris
from sklearn.svm import SVC

iris = load_iris()
X_train, X_test, y_train, y_test = train_test_split(iris.data, iris.target)

param_range = [0.001, 0.01, 0.1, 1, 10, 100]
param_grid = {'C': param_range, 'gamma': param_range}
grid = GridSearchCV(SVC(),
                    param_grid=param_grid,
                    return_train_score=True,
                    cv=10,
                    iid=False)
grid.fit(X_train, y_train)
grid.score(X_test, y_test)

    grid = GridSearchCV(pipe,
